_sText:
Ok i uploaded my second beta of this map which does now include the levels 1 to 4.

have fun playing it, and please send me some feedback that i can improove the map.

if you dont know how make this map work on your server, try this:
type "-tickrate 66; -console" in your launch options of counterstrike source.
when you are on the map type "sv_airaccelerate 150" in the console.
